hoursPlayed:
 for those who like reading visual novels i wouldn't recomend this because of the little dialogue and grindy gameplay; other than that it's not a bad game:)

Cons:
- for a visual novel i felt that the dialogue is really scarce;
- gameplay can get repetitive really fast;
- too 100% i think you need to grind on 1-2 things daily( thus the repetitiveness);
- you have to hunt for the dialogue or you might miss it;

Pros:
- has gameplay;
- an ok story;
- despite little dialogue it is nicely written;
- easy (but long and boring) to 100%;
- nice music and cute Amy voice:));'
- nice graphics;
"

